==Setup==
The following changes need to be made to the standard Legion modules before running this software:<br />

<code>module unload compilers</code><br /><code>module load compilers/gnu/4.9.2</code><br /><code>module load bamtools/2.4.0/gnu-4.9.2</code><br />







